commit.message: Allow composing many packets at once.
Improve router handling of multi-packet messages
Clean up local client handling of multiple messages.  Extract multi-entity deletion to NetSimEntity.
Change remove packet button to an 'X', only show it if more than one packet is present.
Add level config option to show/hide the 'add packet' button
Use font-awesome icon for remove-packet button
Don't hide packet info columns in log
Rename keypress handler generator, stricter check for default values
